	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Q dropped by for approximately half a second to post this at #nesdev: <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.qmtpro.com/~nes/visual2a03/">http://www.qmtpro.com/~nes/visual2a03/</a><!-- m -->
<br />
<br />It's a transistor level JavaScript simulator of 2A03, based on the 6502 simulator that was posted at visual6502.org some time ago. Pretty cool stuff.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
